To Server Operators:
There is a point_servercommand named server_command_kill that just sets airaccel, maxvel, and kicks bots 3 seconds after map spawn.
All filters act as either anti-cheat or as part of a path to an easter egg (s4 and b1). There are no global filtered teleport shenanagins.
